@0 = ~The water clears. A woman in argent armor stands before a door beneath the world. Something waits beyond it—something she knows, or believes she knows. She reaches out. For an instant, you cannot tell whether she is opening the way or being drawn through. Then the water clouds.~
@1 = ~The water remains cloudy. Two Essences of Clarity are needed to clear it.~
@2 = ~The water is still and cloudy. It has nothing more to show you.~
